OL,3,CBereaved parents 'not alone' as
OL,4,Cremembrance weekend held at hospital
OL,6,FA special event has been held in
OL,7,FTorquay for bereaved parents to
OL,8,Fcelebrate and remember the lives of
OL,9,Ftheir child.
OL,11,FTorbay Hospital put on a craft
OL,12,Fworkshop on Saturday 30 November, a
OL,13,Fchance for families to connect with
OL,14,Feach other.
OL,16,FOn Sunday 1 December, a service was
OL,17,Fheld at All Saints Church in
OL,18,FBabbacombe, where hospital staff and
OL,19,Fparents shared their experiences.
