OL,3,CBereaved parents 'not alone' as
OL,4,Cremembrance weekend held at hospital
OL,6,FQuinn Irish was only 12-years-old when
OL,7,Fhe died in December 2022. He suffered
OL,8,Fbrain damage as a baby after
OL,9,Fcontracting a common virus, leaving
OL,10,Fhim with profound learning
OL,11,Fdifficulties and complex medical needs.
OL,13,FDavid Irish, Quinn's father, said:
OL,14,F"There's a certain amount of trauma
OL,15,Fthat comes out, massive grief and
OL,16,Fquestioning. But events like this help
OL,17,Fyou to start to manage that.
OL,19,F"You don't deal with it but you learn
OL,20,Fto live with it. It's emotional but
OL,21,Fit's also Quinn still being with us."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
