OL,3,CBereaved parents 'not alone' as
OL,4,Cremembrance weekend held at hospital
OL,6,FQuinn's mother, Lydia, said: "However
OL,7,Fyou celebrate Christmas, it's a time
OL,8,Ffor family, so it's going to be a time
OL,9,Fwhen people we've lost, are remembered.
OL,11,F"So it feels really appropriate and
OL,12,Fpoignant that there is a seasonal
OL,13,Fevent where we can come together and
OL,14,Fmeet other families."
OL,16,FBecky Jeffery suffered a miscarriage
OL,17,Fat 19 weeks and three days. She says
OL,18,Fthe aftercare her family received from
OL,19,Fthe midwives helped them process the
OL,20,Floss of Oscar.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
