OL,3,CBereaved parents 'not alone' as
OL,4,Cremembrance weekend held at hospital
OL,6,FBecky said: "It was traumatic because
OL,7,FI had to go through the labour. It was
OL,8,Fmy first pregnancy, I didn't know what
OL,9,Fwas going to happen. You know the
OL,10,Finevitable is going to happen as well,
OL,11,Fso it's trying to manage so many
OL,12,Ffeelings.
OL,14,F"We had a little funeral service for
OL,15,FOscar at the hospital and it really
OL,16,Fhelped with the grieving afterwards.
OL,18,F"It's nice knowing you're not alone,
OL,19,Fsocialising with other families and
OL,20,Fwatching the kids have fun. Knowing
OL,21,Fyou are helping each other."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
