OL,3,CBereaved parents 'not alone' as
OL,4,Cremembrance weekend held at hospital
OL,6,FThe remembrance weekend takes place
OL,7,Fannually, with staff from Torbay and
OL,8,FSouth Devon NHS Foundation Trust's
OL,9,Fmaternity unit, chaplaincy services
OL,10,Fand children's community nursing team
OL,11,Forganising the events alongside local
OL,12,Fparents.
